    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. It runs and drives smoothly, with a reliable engine and a clean interior that shows only light signs of use. While the exterior is generally in great shape, you may find a few minor stone chips or very light surface scratches consistent with careful driving. It is a dependable car that is ready for its next owner without needing immediate repairs.",
